                    <h2>Eligibility, fine print, and what changed in 2026</h2>
                    <p>
                      Minimum salary AED 30,000/month. AECB score gating unspecified by ENBD;
                      reader-survey data suggests a 700+ floor. Annual fee waived for the first
                      year on direct application; not on aggregator-referred applications.
