                    <p>Use a personal email, not your work account. Strip metadata from any documents.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="ch">
                    <div class="hd">Signal</div>
                    <div class="addr">+971 5X XXX XX12</div>
                    <p>End-to-end encrypted. Set messages to disappear. We will never reveal who you are without your written consent — even if subpoenaed.</p>
                  </div>
