              <WfHeader />
              <div class="wf-pagehead">
                <div class="crumb">Corrections · running log</div>
                <h1 style="font-size:56px;">Every correction we've made.</h1>
                <p>If we get something wrong, we fix it within 24 hours and log it here. Substantive errors that change a verdict are headlined at the top of the original article and emailed to subscribers in the next Friday Brief. We've published 184 articles in 2025–26; this is the full record of where we've been wrong.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="wf-corr-stats">
